text: Habiba Msika, also spelled Messika (حبيبة مسيكة), (born 1903 Testour – February 21, 1930 Tunis), was a Tunisian singer, dancer and actress. Born Marguerite Msika, she was the niece of singer Leïla Sfez. == References == Category:Tunisian singers Category:Murdered musicians Category:1903 births Category:1930 deaths Category:Deaths from fire Category:Actors from Tunis
